_sText:
So, this one is a small(ish) Fight Yard map, nothing special in it, theres just 5 levels, ladders, and water on the bottom so you can safely jump from the top level to the lowest one.
Had to add a little glass shield on spawns because otherwise everyone would have been constantly spawnkilling others, but thats fixed now.

The map is fy_omen_levels and was created by me.

Other Info; Goal is to annihilate the opposing team and buyzone is included in the map.
